airtrafficcontrol.app

Class AirTrafficControlAppToolbox

  • java.lang.Object
    • airtrafficcontrol.app.AirTrafficControlAppToolbox

  • public class AirTrafficControlAppToolbox
extends java.lang.Object
    Class whose subclasses's instances provide tools for apps of air traffic control. Instances have a flights database and a reports generator.
